{"tid":946502,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【資料庫】摩佬平均得分衰過莫天才","createTime":"2018-12-18T14:32:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T09:20:05.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8357fc71b4c57f8793cfb7b9e23ed2cf705c4d46","tid":946502,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:32:07.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=%2BLAOwWMB1dqzkVwaUobaekbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=a2570ff8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼聯在周二怒炒領隊摩連奴，究竟這位名帥的表現有多差？從以下數字可略知一二。<br />\n<br />\n1.62<br />\n曼聯於摩連奴（Jose Mourinho）麾下平均每場英超取得1.62分，比起莫耶斯年代的1.65分更低。<br />\n<br />\n176<br />\n摩佬帶領曼聯於英超贏得176分，比同時期的曼城（222）、熱刺（202）、車路士（200）、利物浦（196）都少。<br />\n<br />\n29<br />\n摩佬向來自豪的防守今季缺堤，第6位的曼聯至今17場英超失掉29球，比第19位的哈特斯菲爾德失多1球。<br />\n<br />\n83<br />\n防守漏水，曼聯進攻亦啞火，同樣出戰93場聯賽，紅魔僅入151球，同市宿曼城轟入多達234球，足足多83球。<br />\n<br />\n26<br />\n今季曼聯在17場英超過後取得26分，是球會自1990/91球季以來最差的成績。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"438b53ccc2ef943a6dadc27c5917ab481c994208","tid":946502,"uid":16659,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:32:49.000Z","msg":"椰子是無辜的<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34891a065ae51be610119b07cae8d6bc4bb94479","tid":946502,"uid":3194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:37:11.000Z","msg":"原來熱刺都拎左咁多分<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61e6f2b36a3094f62f594f9cc635a9244be27449","tid":946502,"uid":371,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"34891a065ae51be610119b07cae8d6bc4bb94479","tid":946502,"uid":3194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:37:11.000Z","msg":"原來熱刺都拎左咁多分<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"re